  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Abu al-Qasim Ja'far ibn Muhammad -- may God have mercy on him -- reported to me from his father, from Sa'd ibn Abdillah, from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Isa, from Muhammad ibn Sinan, from Abdul Karim ibn Amru and Ibrahim ibn Rahah al-Basri, who both narrated from Mayassar, who said: Abu Abdillah Ja'far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon them both, said to me:",
    "ur": "فرمایا: ابو القاسم جعفر بن محمد... سے میسر نے روایت کی کہ ابو عبد اللہ جعفر بن محمد علیہما السلام نے مجھ سے فرمایا:",
    "tr": "Dedi: Ebu'l-Kasım Cafer bin Muhammed... Meyser'den rivayet edildi ki Ebu Abdullah Cafer bin Muhammed aleyhimesselam bana dedi:",
    "fa": "فرمود: ابوالقاسم جعفر بن محمد... از میسر نقل شد که ابوعبدالله جعفر بن محمد علیهما السلام به من فرمود:",
    "id": "Ia berkata: Abu al-Qasim Ja'far bin Muhammad... dari Mayassar yang berkata: Abu Abdullah Ja'far bin Muhammad AS berkata kepadaku:",
